{"tid":197534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發)日俄關係不沉常 俄羅斯轟炸機、反潛機等共6架軍機迫近日本領空","createTime":"2017-04-12T02:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T02:52:32.000Z","uid":30561,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45ecc0732e9353b83e3b0b28b093dbd199c19aca","tid":197534,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T02:44:07.000Z","msg":"&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 北韓局勢因美國疑似要向北韓動武而緊張,但同時,日俄關係亦不沉常。日本防衛省表示,俄羅斯轟炸機、反潛機等共6架軍機迫近日本領空。<br />\n<br />\n日本防衛省指,6架軍機於當地周二從3個方向陸續飛行,迫近日本領空,日本航空自衛隊戰鬥機因此緊急升空。<br />\n<br />\n日本《產經新聞》報導,俄羅斯軍機幾乎同時從太平洋一側與日本海一側靠近日本的情況,實屬罕見,防衛省正分析俄羅斯的意圖。 (BC)"},{"pid":"e814c33639aa2afc5841088647640b7a06e2d0a1","tid":197534,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T02:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRDTf2FHkkYO7I28o52VAzHpkLVSU_Nn7M3Ztoeot3-QG0dn0Rf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcRDTf2FHkkYO7I28o52VAzHpkLVSU_Nn7M3Ztoeot3-QG0dn0Rf&h=56723ff1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e398a587bf68ac0e490c0466dd0c03a42213cd4a","tid":197534,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T02:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nintchdbpict000272318518.jpg?w=960&amp;strip=all\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2Fnintchdbpict000272318518.jpg%3Fw%3D960%26strip%3Dall&h=16d28b63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fad74126ecf08c3906bda28d4a77f8390aa88a4d","tid":197534,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T02:47:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%A8%B16%E6%9E%B6%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E8%BB%8D%E6%A9%9F%E8%BF%AB%E8%BF%91%E9%A0%98%E7%A9%BA-%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%9B%E9%9A%8A%E5%8D%87%E7%A9%BA%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D-002637992.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.c